game_description: This is Lemur Tag! "Become Lemur Now!" Time has passed, There is no more rainforests, Just scrap metal. This is a Hand Movement Based Game where you are a Lemur! Hangout with your fellow Lemur friends! Get cosmetics, fly in Zero Gravity, whatever your Lemur head desires! Many secrets around maps, interesting areas, Horror? Anything that the community wants, ask and you'll get! Download now to have Lemurs in your mixed reality!
